---
title: Salmon & Polenta Primavera with Bell Pepper, Zucchini, Mushrooms & Grape Tomatoes
description: A colorful mix of bell pepper, zucchini, mushrooms, and grape tomatoes simmers into a saucy veggie jumble, served over flavorful polenta enriched with nutty nutritional yeast. With precooked polenta and quick-sautéed vegetables, this comforting, plant-based dish comes together in no time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/686e419e249cc147aea82971-37843099.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/686e419e249cc147aea82971-en-US.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/salmon-and-polenta-primavera-686e419e249cc147aea82971
course: main course
cuisine: Southern Europe
nutrition:
  calories: 550 kcal
